# Palindrome Number Checker ğŸ”ğŸ”¢

A JavaScript project that checks whether a given number is a **Palindrome** or not.  
A number is called a palindrome if it reads the same **forward and backward**.  
This project is built with a **modern UI** and clean logic, ideal for beginners and interviews.


https://palindrome-number-checker-js-program.netlify.app/


